	<li>
		Significant hands-on work along with team development.</li>
	<li>
		Implement strategic improvements to database infrastructure to lower costs and increase reliability.</li>
</ul>
<p>
	<strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>
<ul>
	<li>
		B.A. or B.Sc. or equivalent.&nbsp;</li>
	<li>
